📝 Instructions for Hassan:

Complete all 4 functions that handle screen transitions and coordinate conversions.

Functions to complete:

    show_main_app() - Switch from start screen to main app
    show_start_screen() - Switch back to start screen
    grid_to_canvas() - Convert math coordinates to pixel positions
    canvas_to_grid() - Convert pixel positions to math coordinates

These handle the UI transitions and coordinate system for the visualization! 📊
